roto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Metody</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Metoda <code><strong>toString()</strong></code> zwraca łańcuch znaków reprezentujący daną tablicę wraz z jej elementami.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> months <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'Styczeń'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Luty'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Marzec'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Kwiecień'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nmonths<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toString</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// \"Styczeń,Luty,Marzec,Kwiecień\"</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sk.c5.82adnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code><var>arr</var>.toString()</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parametry","title":"Parametry","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Brak.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"opis","title":"Opis","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Obiekt <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array\"><code>Array</code></a> przesłania metodę <code>toString</code> obiektu <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a>. Dla obiektów Array, metoda <code>toString</code> łączy tablicę i zwraca jeden łańcuch znaków zawierający wszystkie elementy tablicy oddzielone przecinkami. Przykładowo poniższy kod tworzy tablicę i stosuje metodę <code>toString</code>, aby przekształcić tablicę do łańcucha znaków.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> monthNames <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Jan\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Feb\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Mar\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Apr\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> myVar <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> monthNames<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toString</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// przypisuje \"Jan,Feb,Mar,Apr\" do zmiennej myVar</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>JavaScript wywołuje metodę <code>toString</code> automatycznie, gdy tablica jest traktowana jako wartość tekstowa lub kiedy istnieje odniesienie do tej tablicy wewnątrz połączonego łańcucha znaków.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"zobacz_tak.c5.bce","title":"Zobacz także","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toSource()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array/join\"><code>Array.prototype.join()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Składnia","id":"sk.c5.82adnia"},{"text":"Opis","id":"opis"},{"text":"Zobacz także","id":"zobacz_tak.c5.bce"}],"summary":"Metoda toString() zwraca łańcuch znaków reprezentujący daną tablicę wraz z jej elementami.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Array.prototype.toString()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Array.prototype.toString()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Array.prototype.toString()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Array.prototype.toString()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Array.prototype.toString()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Array.prototype.toString()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Array.prototype.toString()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Array.prototype.toString()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Array.prototype.toString()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Array.prototype.toString()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/array/tostring","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/array/tostring/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/